[SN]TITLE[SN]
Is this the wackiest inventor ever?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Have you ever wished you could invent a machine to make life a bit easier - maybe make your toast in the morning, or pour your glass of orange juice?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
23 September 2016 Last updated at 07:44 BST
Well that's exactly what Joseph Herscher from New York in America does.
He started off by inventing a machine to store his sweets when he was only five-years-old - and his wacky inventions took off from there!
Ricky's been finding out about his bizarre inventions...
